descript.abstract: Dam sites within the state of Idaho. Information includes dam name, section, storage capacity, height, reservoir surface area, as well as other information. This layer was generated from the Dam Safety database of Dams. This file was updated August 2010. There is additional information in the dam safety database including additional fields not seen in this layer.

dataIdInfo.idAbs: Dam locations within the state of Idaho. Information includes dam name, Township/Range/Section description, storage capacity, height, reservoir surface area, spill type, spill depth, outlet type, release capacity, condition, inspection date, as well as other information. See the supplemental information for the complete list of attributes. This coverage was generated from Sonny Hornbakers database of Active Dams. This file was updated Nov 2010. There is additional information in the dam safety database including additional fields not seen in this shapefile as well as locations of proposed dams, abandoned or undersized dams and breeched dams. Some dam locations were established using gps. Most points were digitized at a scale of 1:24,000
